%% Data Flow Diagram - Complete System

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant Landing as 🎨 Landing Page
    participant Frontend as ⚛️ React Frontend
    participant API as 🔌 Django API
    participant Agent1 as 🤖 Agent 1<br/>Classification
    participant Agent2 as 🤖 Agent 2<br/>Extraction
    participant Agent3 as 🤖 Agent 3<br/>Validation
    participant Agent4 as 🤖 Agent 4<br/>Routing
    participant Agent5 as 🤖 Agent 5<br/>Audit
    participant Gemini as 🧠 Gemini AI
    participant MongoDB as 🗄️ MongoDB
    participant Storage as 📦 Storage
    participant Reviewer as 👨‍💼 Reviewer

    %% User Journey
    User->>Landing: Visit Landing Page
    Landing->>User: Display Features & Demo
    User->>Landing: Click "Launch Demo"
    Landing->>Frontend: Redirect to App

    %% Authentication
    User->>Frontend: Login (customer_demo)
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/auth/login/
    API->>MongoDB: Verify Credentials
    MongoDB-->>API: User Data
    API-->>Frontend: JWT Token
    Frontend-->>User: Dashboard

    %% Document Upload
    User->>Frontend: Upload Document
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/documents/upload-url/
    API-->>Frontend: Presigned Upload URL
    Frontend->>Storage: Upload File (Direct)
    Storage-->>Frontend: Upload Complete
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/documents/upload/ (Finalize)
    
    %% Agent Workflow Trigger
    API->>Agent1: Trigger Workflow
    
    %% Agent 1: Classification
    Agent1->>Storage: Read Document
    Storage-->>Agent1: Document Data
    Agent1->>Gemini: Classify Document Type
    Gemini-->>Agent1: Classification Result
    Agent1->>MongoDB: Store Classification
    Agent1->>Agent2: Pass to Extraction

    %% Agent 2: Extraction
    Agent2->>Storage: Read Document Pages
    Agent2->>Gemini: Extract Fields
    Gemini-->>Agent2: Structured Data
    Agent2->>MongoDB: Store Extraction
    Agent2->>Agent3: Pass to Validation

    %% Agent 3: Validation
    Agent3->>MongoDB: Get Policy Rules
    Agent3->>Gemini: Validate Fields
    Gemini-->>Agent3: Validation Result
    Agent3->>MongoDB: Store Validation
    Agent3->>Agent4: Pass to Routing

    %% Agent 4: Routing
    Agent4->>Gemini: Analyze Risk
    Gemini-->>Agent4: Routing Decision
    
    alt Low Risk - Auto Approve
        Agent4->>MongoDB: Mark as Approved
        Agent4->>Agent5: Pass to Audit
    else Medium Risk - Review Needed
        Agent4->>MongoDB: Create Review Task
        Agent4->>Reviewer: Send Email Notification
        Agent4->>Agent5: Pass to Audit
        
        %% Human Review Loop
        Reviewer->>Frontend: Access Review Queue
        Frontend->>API: GET /api/reviews/
        API->>MongoDB: Fetch Reviews
        MongoDB-->>API: Review Data
        API-->>Frontend: Review List
        Reviewer->>Frontend: Approve/Reject
        Frontend->>API: POST /api/reviews/{id}/submit/
        API->>MongoDB: Update Review Status
        API->>Agent5: Trigger Audit Update
    else High Risk - Exception
        Agent4->>MongoDB: Create Exception
        Agent4->>Reviewer: Send Alert
        Agent4->>Agent5: Pass to Audit
    end

    %% Agent 5: Audit
    Agent5->>MongoDB: Gather All Stage Data
    Agent5->>Gemini: Generate Audit Summary
    Gemini-->>Agent5: Audit Report
    Agent5->>MongoDB: Store Audit Log
    Agent5->>API: Workflow Complete

    %% Status Update
    API-->>Frontend: Status Update (WebSocket/Polling)
    Frontend-->>User: Show Processing Complete

    %% User Views Result
    User->>Frontend: View Document Status
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/documents/{id}/
    API->>MongoDB: Fetch Document Data
    MongoDB-->>API: Complete Document Info
    API-->>Frontend: Document Details
    Frontend-->>User: Display Results
